This virus is deadly it has a 3.4% mortality rate, meaning it is more lethal than the Spanish flu which killed about 50 to 100 million in just two years (Spanish flu just had about 2% mortality rate). Corona virus is also quite a fast spreader.

In South Korea from 1 person on January 20, 2020 it then spread to 20 people in one month (February 20, 2020), people might think this is slow, but if you look at it again:

From 20 people on February 20, 2020 it has now spread to 6284 people in just about two weeks !

One thing people can do is to not touch their faces with their hands (this is according to WHO). The second best thing is: if they really really need to touch their face right now and it so happened that they do not have sanitizer or gloves or washroom nearby, then simply touch it with your upper arms, lower arms or shoulders, this will at least reduce the risk of contracting the disease.
